Program: Start the Week
Title: 06/04/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00jh4f5
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 6 Apr 2009
Andrew Marr talks to former minister in the post-war Iraqi government Ali Allawi and actor-playwright Wallace Shawn. Plus Marina Hyde on how celebrities turn political and Lewis Wolpert on the secret life of cells. Wolpert maintains that for their size, cells are the most complex objects in the universe. Show less